Interface AclfPSXformer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AclfBranchAdapter, AclfXformer, BranchRef<AclfBranch>, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier

    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AclfPSXformerImpl, AcscPSXformerImpl

    public interface AclfPSXformer
extends AclfXformer
    A representation of the model object 'PS Xfr Adapter'. An adapter to convert an AclfBranch object to a PSXfr branch.
